{"tid":1443621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽]  上街係為爭取五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T10:30:06.000Z","uid":171718,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bdd232fac120680eeb8e8c1200300dde3618d9","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要清楚：<br />\n<br />\n手足上街係為爭取五大訴求 <br />\n去北角搞紅衫同五大訴求完全無關係<br />\n而且保護市民係警方責任<br />\n如果再發生無差別打人就反證元朗同北角都有警黑勾結特登唔保護市民<br />\n<br />\n所以任何有人叫我地去搞鳩班紅衫 要屌曬佢地老母<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b748193a6748e775925c8b5ddea22b47111df7ab","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2577b633b886cb2154ed52447b121450adbb2601","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72774cb5ce3bc674d002c6bf85e778f8871c3632","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e969bae742c683a218ced32dddd2a210f9baffa3","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9728ab8d8853519ff294dbf34b6f21e59257146","tid":1443621,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"<im